description:
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking enthusiastic and highly motivated individuals to join our busy team. The successful candidate will be able to demonstrate excellent verbal/written communication and interpersonal skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate must be able to work flexible days/sessions across 3 sites. Hours to be worked over Monday – Sunday including evening clinics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous Outpatient experience would be advantageous but not essential as training will be provided. A knowledge of medical and surgical nursing would be desirable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an excellent opportunity to become part of a truly dynamic team helping to shape the future of Outpatient Services. Outpatient clinics are fast paced and offer variety and learning opportunities for Staff to develop their knowledge and skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Shift pattern: Monday – Sunday including evening clinics&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hours: Various.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
